ce on the Farm Bill Neither House is in accord with the Secretary of Agriculture nor the President and the indica tions are that the Secretary and the President are not fully agreed The feeling between the North and the South over the antilynch bill is bitter and as the day for final action approaches the situa Would Bes mo the Will Bes There are two classes of people in the worldthe would be rich who are always wishing and the will be rich who are steadily saving In which class eare you We invite you to join the will bes by opening and building up a savings account Citizens Bank Trust Co QUINCY FLORIDA MEMBER FEDERAL DEPOSIT INSURANCE CORPORATION JEivPiy iwbefler liqhTT beHer tighter The Ideal CHRISTMAS GIFT YOUR most perplexing gift prob lem is now solved with one of these modern I E S glareless Lamps These new scientifically designed I E S Lamps provide just the right amount of glareless illumination"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-01-27T17:02:10.527Z", "group": ["ndnp/fu", "university-of-florida-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn95047334/1937-12-16/ed-1/?sp=2", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:fu:batch_fu_hastings_ver02:data:sn95047334:00529042401:1937121601:0852/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=475&w=325", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:fu:batch_fu_hastings_ver02:data:sn95047334:00529042401:1937121601:0852/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=951&w=650", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/fu/batch_fu_hastings_ver02/data/sn95047334/00529042401/1937121601/0852.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 2, "language": ["english"], "location": ["gadsden county", "quincy", "united states", "florida", "gadsden"], "location_city": ["quincy"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["gadsden"], "location_state": ["florida"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "ap